/-!
# W34 exact Figure witness source

This file names the precise source layer behind the W32 exact Figure row
assembly.  The selected Figure 8/Figure 9 witnesses are not extracted from
frame/cyclic rows alone; they are extracted from the W22 local exact angle
data for the Lemma 8 family generated by those rows.

The main theorem below records the sharp missing statement: for a fixed
frame/cyclic source, W32 exact Figure rows are missing exactly when that W22
local exact angle-data extraction is missing.
-/

noncomputable section

namespace ErdosProblems1066
namespace Swanepoel
namespace ExactFigureWitnessSourceW34

open FigureAngleSourceInhabitationW21
